扮撚晒大少，乜春都唔屌<br />\n死翻去現實就見到舊肥豬肉都扯旗<br />\n成世人連女人都未摸過<br />\n慘情到要日日對住AV打飛機<br />\n晚晚係高登同d人妖娘娘調情<br />\n唔好講話比欣宜你地屌唔屌<br />\n我諗比個白韻琴你地d毒男都成班餓狗搶屎咁搶住屌呀白小姐呀！"},{"pid":"ca713ba4dfd8004eb844546673c5d61019188f3d","tid":793303,"uid":21924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:50:19.000Z","msg":"你食飯撈唔撈屎<br />\nYes or 撈"},{"pid":"a2cc20b56c22b72b7e06a095f3408060f43aa547","tid":793303,"uid":46842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T13:51:20.000Z","msg":"睇左3段已經係極限"},{"pid":"76389e58c6620ce07b431c7e3652c4edcf2228cd","tid":793303,"uid":134666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:00:59.000Z","msg":"3/10 (字數分) 堆砌的情節"},{"pid":"cb790115cdf5731e1bb7ec581181cd9f5b282ef9","tid":793303,"uid":182608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:06:34.000Z","msg":"文筆有待改善"},{"pid":"f568f69b11026756f426f5f964112880d422238c","tid":793303,"uid":115344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:21:22.000Z","msg":"好尷尬"},{"pid":"a359f7d29e9cd1f2dd3e372c5473ebc9f595d7a3","tid":793303,"uid":22855,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:24:22.000Z","msg":"好笑喎  樓上做乜撚野"},{"pid":"fd671fee8ef55999d2a6710cd997a3f5ce2ac398","tid":793303,"uid":41130,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"多屎 多士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾好笑"},{"pid":"38cedd170daa31f8bd668cdc9635dc926717ae53","tid":793303,"uid":6739,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T14:30:34.000Z","msg":"幾好<br />\n等達哥聲演加黎特連環圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2321bdb17cdc05feb1943696c20a1bfbe02f61bb","tid":793303,"uid":8949,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea62266e0472112bfbb6f1b706bec55f18c6ec3e","tid":793303,"uid":40847,"like":46,"dislike":21,"score":25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T10:36:08.00